* 1984–1988 : {{ENG-d}} [[Liverpool FC]]
* 1988–1990 : {{ENG-d}} [[Ipswich Town Football Club]]
* 1990–1991 : {{ENG-d}} [[Middlesbrough FC]]
* 1991–1997 : {{ENG-d}} [[Ipswich Town Football Club]]

